    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成為燒烤大師！與朋友在大自然中烹調美味的燒烤，最多可容納 5 人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/1ec977ae2d0a5bfc5d491ca0ec693048.poster.avif?t=1759166534\" width=498 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/1ec977ae2d0a5bfc5d491ca0ec693048.webm?t=1759166534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/1ec977ae2d0a5bfc5d491ca0ec693048.mp4?t=1759166534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-🍖 逐步**燒烤的創作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖 ***食譜的變化**。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖 透過螢幕，您會**嗅到**燒烤的香味</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖 您可以**踢**煩人的朋友，讓他們談論簡單的事情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索用多種不同食材製作燒烤的藝術：甚至可以拿兔肉用香蕉蘸醬油醃漬！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >對了，別忘了在烹煮後享用燒烤本身！</p>",
